Just ahead of Black Friday, Apple is offering an Apple TV promotion for new and returning subscribers. Eligible customers can get six months of Apple TV for just &#36;5.99 per month.<br/>
<br/>
<img src="https://images.macrumors.com/article-new/2025/10/Apple-TV-Color.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="900" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1023382" /><br/>
After the six-month period, the subscription price will increase to &#36;12.99, which is the regular price for the Apple TV service.<br/>
<br/>
At &#36;5.99 per month, Apple is discounting Apple TV by over 50 percent. The deal will be available from November 21 to December 1 <a href="https://tv.apple.com/offer/tvs.sbd.4000?itscg=10000&itsct=atv-apl-tv-op-learn_more-BF-112125">on the Apple TV website</a>.<br/>
<br/>
